        <h2 style="border-bottom:1px solid #888;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;">Core Skills</h2><p style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;">Languages:  Python (Advanced) • Java • JavaScript • SQL • AI &amp; LLM Orchestration:  LangGraph • LangChain • Multi-Agent Systems • GPT-4o/Vision • Claude 3.5 Sonnet • Ol- • lama • Prompt Engineering (CoT • ReAct) • Structured Output Validation (Pydantic) • LangSmith • Machine Learning:  Scikit-learn • XGBoost • LightGBM • Random Forest • SVM • Feature Engineering • SMOTE/ADASYN • Explainable AI (SHAP • LIME) • Model Drift Monitoring • Deep Learning &amp; NLP:  PyTorch • CNN • LSTM • Transformers • BERT</p>
