            <p style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;"><strong>and compliance issues — deployed on edge AI devices, reducing manual shelf audit time by 45%.</strong><br>Partnered with product and data engineering teams to define evaluation metrics and track model performance post-<br>deployment.</p>
