            <p style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;"><strong>daily transactions at 94% precision.</strong><br>Built a high-dimensional feature pipeline using SQL and Pandas to extract 50+ behavioral indicators, improving<br>detection of sophisticated fraud patterns by 20%.<br>Resolved extreme class imbalance using cost-sensitive learning and SMOTE/ADASYN, achieving 0.89 AUC-ROC on<br>production transaction data.<br>Integrated SHAP and LIME for explainable AI outputs, generating human-readable reasoning codes for flagged trans-<br>actions to streamline manual audit workflows.<br>Deployed fraud models as Dockerized FastAPI microservices, maintaining sub-100ms response times under peak load.<br>Built an MLflow + CI/CD retraining loop with drift monitoring and A/B testing, reducing false negatives by 60%<br>over 12 months.<br>Built an OCR pipeline using Tesseract, Hugging Face Transformers, and Azure Cognitive Services to extract and<br>classify data from invoices and contracts, achieving 91% extraction accuracy and cutting manual data entry by 55%.</p>
